songs.title: Le Horde (Intro)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse: Tech N9ne & Krizz Kaliko]
Who's the number one independent rapper in the world?
(N9na)
Who’s the man we call Technician Number One?
(N9na)
Who created the medicine to navigate through the darkness?
(N9na)
Who provided us with his good word, decade after decade, with love?
(N9na)
Somebody say N9na?
(N9na)
N9na
(N9na)
What's his name?
(N9na)
One more time
(N9na)
Strange Music 20 year anniversary
Here we go again
